{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778547145758,"sessionID":"ses_1e65e38f4ffe9ucxqID2SRwgIL","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"chatcmpl-tool-920ed0ddc67e9f5a","state":{"status":"error","input":{"command":"deep-research-specialist","prompt":"Research the 'medial prefrontal cortex' to provide a scientifically grounded definition and associated PMIDs for use in the UBERON ontology. \n\nThe request from issue #3446 mentions it's composed of BA12, BA25, and anterior cingulate cortex (BA32, BA33, BA24).\n\nPlease find:\n1. A precise anatomical definition.\n2. One or more peer-reviewed publications (PMIDs) that support this definition.\n3. Verification of its parent terms (prefrontal cortex, regional part of brain).\n\nReturn a summary with the recommended definition and PMIDs.","subagent_type":"general"},"error":"The task tool was called with invalid arguments: SchemaError(Missing key\n  at [\"description\"]).\nPlease rewrite the input so it satisfies the expected schema.","time":{"start":1778547145754,"end":1778547145756}},"id":"prt_e19abaf0b001DUVSzdYPwKlhXI","sessionID":"ses_1e65e38f4ffe9ucxqID2SRwgIL","messageID":"msg_e19ab9938001yAdPa4R8Mbbf4C"}}
